 integrated process\nincluding both methods would eliminate the communication gap between users and\ndevelopers at early stages of the development process and mitigates the risk of\nrequirements change in later stages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jul 2017 16:36:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-18"}
