inside of a biwreath. Choosing different distributive\nlaws and different 2-cells $\\lambda$ in a biwreath, leads to different and\npossibly new algebraic constructions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jul 2017 03:14:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Jul 2017 01:38:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Aug 2017 20:09:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-11"}
