es down to\n100 pL in a measurement time of 3 hours. Spectral resolutions of 0.01 ppm in\nliquids and of 0.1 ppm in the investigated biological entities are\ndemonstrated. The obtained results indicate a promising route for NMR studies\nat the single unit level of important sub-nL biological entities, such as\nliving microscopic organisms and eggs of several mammalians, humans included.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jul 2017 07:04:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
