 effective range measurement. These results are\ndiscussed in the light of neuronal evolution, where the coexistence of coherent\nand incoherent dynamics during the developmental stage is particularly likely.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jul 2017 07:41:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-10"}
